Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,曾經有個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Once there was a man
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.71,0:00:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,想要找出地球的真實年齡\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who went searching for the true age of the earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,經過他的努力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In his struggles to discover it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他無意間發現了一個極大的威脅\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he stumbled on a grave threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,1966年 加州 帕薩迪納 春季的某一天\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Beautiful spring day, Pasadena, California. 1966.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,人們安居樂業\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Business is booming, life's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一個人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Except for one man,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,名叫克萊爾·彼得森的地質化學家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}a geochemist named Clair Patterson,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.76,0:00:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,朋友叫他派特\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}known as Pat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.30,0:00:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,他認為他所看到的所有人都身處於無形的威脅中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He knows that everyone he sees is in danger from an invisible menace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他決心要阻止這一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And he's determined to put a stop to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不計代價\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}no matter what the cost.
